<emphasis id="B97DEA9E924C772EFAABFA1AFF29BA48" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="181">Reginato 1277</emphasis>
; G: 
<emphasis id="B97DEA9E924C772EFF1DFA3EFE14BA48" box="[227,389,1518,1539]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="181">Amorim 6559; H</emphasis>
